.aminet-dir
game/role
.type
Role-Playing Game
.short
Non-graphical interactive fiction game
.description
Demo version of a classic fantasy interactive fiction game with an
excellent parser that comes close to Infocom quality. The game allows
you to control five characters with different abilities.
.version
1.4
.date
1994.08.15
.author
Rüdiger Hanke
.restrictions
This demo version doesn't allow you to save or restore your game position,
and the story is limited.
.requirements
Requires OS1.3 and 1 MByte RAM.
